    <h2>Magnesium Gummies vs Pills vs Powder</h2>

    <p>The delivery format you choose affects dose flexibility, cost, taste, and convenience — but not bioavailability. Magnesium is absorbed through the gastrointestinal tract regardless of whether it arrives as a gummy, capsule, tablet, or powder. The key variable is always the amount of elemental magnesium per serving and the specific form of magnesium used.</p>

